{"tid":2174154,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「泡菜戰線」韓星李孝利想改「毛」做藝名被指辱華 網民：你算個屁啊","createTime":"2020-08-25T17:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T18:37:56.000Z","uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"69a30fc3e0d1db802de9d436df2deba7e29f1ccd","tid":2174154,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"「加速主義」<br />\n依家班中國人不斷喺李孝利IG係咁狂咬<br />\n大家快啲幫手留言撐佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hyoleehyolee/?hl=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhyoleehyolee%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hk&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=471c5434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hyoleehyolee/?hl=zh-hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200824/DKUF64HY3JAWZHR5MS44EWSERM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200824%2FDKUF64HY3JAWZHR5MS44EWSERM%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9d0ca702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200824%2FDKUF64HY3JAWZHR5MS44EWSERM%2F&h=2c404bb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200824/DKUF64HY3JAWZHR5MS44EWSERM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nE0zrc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnE0zrc4.jpg&h=2c2bc5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國性感女星李孝利近日因在節目上說了一個字，竟敲碎一眾小粉紅的「玻璃心」，被指是侮辱中共前領導人毛澤東，隨時被內地觀眾封殺。<br />\n<br />\n本月22日，南韓播出節目《玩甚麼好呢？》，李孝利和劉在錫討論是否要取「藝名」，李孝利表示，自己的藝名想要走中國風，因為有可能走向世界，之後她說出「마오」，即「毛」的讀音）怎麼樣？」劉在錫聽後尷尬笑了，而畫面字幕也打上「不要用這個」。節目一出即惹來小粉紅喪鬧，有指，該片已下架。<br />\n<br />\n中國網民狠批「李孝利辱華」，這五個字甚至成為熱搜字眼。李孝利久未使用的微博也被大批內地瘋狂留言，紛紛表示，「孝利姐姐，聽說你想姓毛啊，你知道自己幾斤幾兩嗎，你算個屁啊」、「你給毛提鞋都不配！」、「新浪應該直接封辱華人的號吧」、「毛爺爺不僅是中國的偉人，也是全世界無產階級勞動人民的導師，不知道李女士算是哪位？」、「希望朝鮮早日統一南韓」。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n蕭玉為骨 ：給我上熱搜，限韓令永久好嗎<br />\n真佛了：李孝利不會還有人洗白吧？再說一遍，在國外，mao特指毛爺爺。說實話，韓國給他提鞋都不配<br />\n我我我lxy：毛爺爺是底線。奶奶了個腳，天堂有路你不走，地獄無門你偏要闖。<br />\n夏嗚嗚噫：我想你可以消失了<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"1e70b19c0a5330ceb41e0cb419a510339f5ab50f","tid":2174154,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"大家真係幫手要喺IG幫拖<br />\n中國人太多 佢哋而家好似成班喪屍咁喺李孝利IG進攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRbfaHU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRbfaHU.png&h=c22f1fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDVr1Pz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDVr1Pz.png&h=1eaff1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUu06gf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUu06gf.png&h=edeffe6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"194f020ae9b1c4427b922c8eff182362167247d2","tid":2174154,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e486643420772776f59c0eb6d2ec8eabb85a45","tid":2174154,"uid":193596,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"加速主義就由班小粉紅柒出國際啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d9da17d643f9a8a08626f4b045080b30bb54c5","tid":2174154,"uid":258192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a5e486643420772776f59c0eb6d2ec8eabb85a45","tid":2174154,"uid":193596,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"加速主義就由班小粉紅柒出國際啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"習大大重話要訪韓 點訪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d37e